        "changelog": "<h4>[1.12] 2024\/03\/03<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Added nonce when sorting.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.11<\/h4>\n<p>Supported WordPress 6.4.<br \/>\nPHP 8.0 is now required.<\/p>\n<h4>1.10<\/h4>\n<p>Supported High Performance Order Storage(COT).<\/p>\n<h4>1.09<\/h4>\n<p>Supported WordPress 6.1.<\/p>\n<h4>1.08<\/h4>\n<p>Fixed a problem with duplicate names in %name% tags.<\/p>\n<h4>1.07<\/h4>\n<p>Fixed a problem with the order selection screen when making a refund.<\/p>\n<h4>1.06<\/h4>\n<p>Fixed pagination hook.<\/p>\n<h4>1.05<\/h4>\n<p>Fixed a problem with user filter.<br \/>\nFixed a problem with products filter.<br \/>\nMoved the position of pagination.<\/p>\n<h4>1.04<\/h4>\n<p>Fixed a pagination problem when searching for text.<\/p>\n<h4>1.03<\/h4>\n<p>Supported WordPress 5.7.<\/p>\n<h4>1.02<\/h4>\n<p>Fixed uninstall.<\/p>\n<h4>1.01<\/h4>\n<p>Fixed translation.<\/p>\n<h4>1.00<\/h4>\n<p>Initial release.<\/p>\n",
